title: 1.12.2CatSever空岛端不刷怪
author: yangshuozxc
txt_content: 服务器右键刷怪蛋或者刷怪笼，是可以刷怪的但不自动生成怪物。请求解决

replies.author: xmdhs
replies.txt_content:
输入 /gamerule doMobSpawning 

若显示 false

则输入 /gamerule doMobSpawning true

replies.author: yangshuozxc
replies.txt_content:
xmdhs 发表于 2020-2-5 20:03
